{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2093, "height": 2850, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [168, 750, 247, 1480], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "二九五", "block_bbox": [186, 2140, 239, 2264], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "孟村", "block_bbox": [1021, 254, 1253, 320], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "孟村位于果园乡东北端，渑池县城东南5公里。东邻千秋矿风井，西邻南阎国防公路，南邻县乡公路，北邻富达热电厂。孟村地下煤炭资源丰富，分别是千秋、耿村两大煤矿的煤田。二十世纪八十年代经过个体煤矿大规模开采，至今已有近三十年，有力地支援了国家的经济建设。孟村下辖十个自然村，至2006年底，孟村共有180户850人，其中劳动力470人，从业人员500人，土地面积250公顷，耕地面积150公顷，粮食播种面积160公顷，总产量800吨（其中夏粮498吨）。", "block_bbox": [343, 395, 1908, 784], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜氏所居的下沟是孟村村委会和孟村小学的所在地，也是邹家洼搬迁和新农村建设的希望之地。孟村杜氏为渑池杜氏流芳公支系，始祖为十三世书森，其世系父以上失传。于清咸丰年间从渑池县城迁居孟村，前辈以经商起家，坟茔在孟村下沟。\n", "block_bbox": [341, 803, 1902, 1057], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "2000年孟村杜姓共47人其中男19人，女28人。2008年孟村杜姓49人，其中男20人，女29人。\n", "block_bbox": [346, 1075, 1898, 1195], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "其世系为：", "block_bbox": [422, 1215, 625, 1265], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "流芳公—失传—失传—失传—失传—失传—失传——失传—失传—失传—失传—失传——书森\n", "block_bbox": [346, 1282, 1895, 1403], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9520211815834045, "coordinate": [343.221435546875, 395.14